ening in pittsburgh the northpointe data center located near pittsburgh has received accolades for observing energy efficiency protocols the company has approximately  it employees in the us and approximately  globally it historical information  • throughout  the company underwent a large virtualization intiative involving its hp blade servers being virtualized with a combination of vmware citrix and hyperv technologies • the company upgraded to windows  across its  users in  •  pb data volume companywide across  to  data centers and expects an annual data growth of  •  of its servers are to be virtualized by the end of  • corporate it manages  mobile devices while  are managed elsewhere • corporate it manages  desktops • standardized on  product vendors with a limited set of hardware • data center strategy is centered on standardizing on rackmount x systems and virtualized servers • long term plan for running new applications is to add servers and virtualize but no new facilities are scheduled • less than  of it staff is dedicated to the sustenance of its erp platform • expects around  releasesupdates a year with its current erp solution • the bank of new york mellon corporation has the following security safeguards in place regular policy reviews inventory of personal employee and customer data inventory of locations where data is stored documented incident response process inventory of third parties encryption of mobile devices malware and virus protection software on all devices incident response processes are documented and a continuous compliance model is in place operating under hipaa pcidss  isoiec  nist  compliance standards • the company uses an outsourced provider to monitor threats across its networks security devices and data  • the company began the digital workplace initiative which was designed to improve employee experience through a reduction of dowtime failures and help desk calls this was achieved analyzing unstructured internal data through the 